        <item>
            <title>荒蛮的歌</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_418b0a030102e134.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
用莫名的伤感涂鸦着快乐</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">

</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
我来了</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
为了一点自尊</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
我用缄默回答着太阳</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
云在飞</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
我却在等待</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
我把自己的魂魄留在了山的那边</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
水的这边</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
痴痴的走肉</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
在混沌的胎记中</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
寻找着孕育的折磨</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
我走了</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
在欲望的颠簸中</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
用那个沾满狐疑的萤火</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
点燃孤独的油灯</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
在深邃的夜里</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
诵读走出迷城的歌谣</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
当太阳升起的早晨</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
望着没有灵魂的躯体</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
在城脚下喘着最后的粗气</SPAN></P>]]></description>
