        <item>
            <title>这个春天，会很冷</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_418b0a030102e111.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
找一束干瘪的草</SPAN><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">

</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
埋在冻土里</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
看着划落的日历</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
有暖阳的日子里</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
会有油绿</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
也许那被我埋起来的干草</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
也会发芽</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
但我已经无法分清</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
哪是那束我在冬季埋下的干草</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
一杯清茶</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
凉了</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
喝茶的人</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
走了</SPAN></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
一片飘落的绿叶</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
卷曲的叶尖</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
已经干黄</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
落在只有点点温度的茶前</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
几滴早来的雨</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
带来走去的凉意</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
这个春天</SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
也许会冷</SPAN></P>]]></description>
            <author>闲梦远</author>
